WEBVTT

00:00.793 --> 00:02.461
[♪ opening theme song playing]

00:34.451 --> 00:38.580
JUJUTSU KAISEN

01:30.758 --> 01:33.677
[echoing footsteps]

01:39.224 --> 01:42.352
JUJUTSU KAISEN

01:42.394 --> 01:44.063
[NAOYA] Well, look who it is.

01:44.103 --> 01:46.648
And what an ugly face
you've got there.

01:46.690 --> 01:48.734
I'm pretty sure
it's beyond fixing.

01:48.776 --> 01:50.360
What are you planning
to do, Maki?

01:50.402 --> 01:52.029
[birds chirping]

01:52.071 --> 01:54.239
[MAKI] You mean you can actually
tell women apart by their faces?

01:54.656 --> 01:56.575
I thought
you only saw their asses.

02:01.538 --> 02:03.999
[♪ discordant notes play]

02:05.584 --> 02:07.795
[NAOYA] I'm asking you
what you're going to do.

02:07.836 --> 02:09.671
So answer me,
you piece of trash.

02:09.713 --> 02:13.132
You can't use sorcery.
You can't see cursed spirits.

02:13.174 --> 02:15.803
The looks you had
going for you are ruined.

02:15.844 --> 02:19.514
No one is ever going to
pay attention to you again.

02:19.556 --> 02:22.350
- [Maki sobbing]
- Such a sad situation.

02:22.810 --> 02:24.937
Shall I bully you
like I used to?

02:24.979 --> 02:27.564
[Maki sobbing]

02:27.606 --> 02:29.232
[NAOYA] What are you
going to do?

02:29.274 --> 02:31.693
Cling to the shadow
of Okkotsu or Megumi?

02:34.989 --> 02:37.658
Say something, trash.

02:37.699 --> 02:41.745
[MAKI AND MAI’S MOTHER] Maki.
Come back. Have you forgotten?

02:42.329 --> 02:44.665
You know very well that
we're not allowed entry

02:44.706 --> 02:46.333
into the Forbidden Vault.

02:47.375 --> 02:49.920
Don't worry, the clan head
gave me permission.

02:49.962 --> 02:51.463
[keys clinking]

02:51.505 --> 02:53.882
[MEGUMI]
Head of the Zen'in Clan?

02:53.924 --> 02:55.676
- [MEGUMI] Me?
- [MAKI] Yeah.

02:55.717 --> 02:57.385
It was in Naobito's will.

02:57.427 --> 02:59.638
[MEGUMI] No, thanks.
It'll just be a hassle.

02:59.680 --> 03:01.264
[MAKI]
I think you should accept.

03:01.306 --> 03:02.724
Naobito said
he would entrust

03:02.766 --> 03:04.685
all of the Zen'in Clan's
assets to you,

03:04.726 --> 03:07.270
both the money
and the cursed tools.

03:07.312 --> 03:08.897
If you become head of the clan,

03:08.939 --> 03:11.150
you'll be able to get info
on the big three families

03:11.190 --> 03:12.818
and their headquarters.

03:12.860 --> 03:15.320
It'll make a huge difference in
what we can do from here on out.

03:15.362 --> 03:17.572
[MEGUMI] Sounds like
you should do it, Maki.

03:17.614 --> 03:18.699
You can have it.

03:18.740 --> 03:20.325
Yeah, well, no one's
going to accept me

03:20.367 --> 03:21.326
as the head of the clan.

03:21.368 --> 03:22.828
No one's gonna follow me yet.

03:22.870 --> 03:26.081
The fact is, you possess
the hereditary technique,

03:26.123 --> 03:28.249
and you can activate
your domain.

03:28.291 --> 03:30.794
And you received
lots of attention from Satoru,

03:30.836 --> 03:32.671
yet they would
barely accept you.

03:33.505 --> 03:35.382
Why do I need their acceptance?

03:35.423 --> 03:36.842
Does it even matter
what the members

03:36.884 --> 03:38.593
of the Zen'in Clan
think about it?

03:39.136 --> 03:41.680
You get all those benefits
if you became the head, too,

03:41.722 --> 03:43.140
so just do it already.

03:43.932 --> 03:45.433
[MAKI] It's too soon.

03:45.475 --> 03:46.810
Can't be me yet.

03:49.063 --> 03:51.815
I wouldn't be able
to create a place for Mai.

03:57.154 --> 03:58.488
[MEGUMI] All right, fine.

03:58.530 --> 04:02.117
[MAKI AND MAI’S MOTHER]
Come back here!

04:07.873 --> 04:09.332
Tell me why?

04:09.374 --> 04:12.711
Tell me why must you
always be like this, Maki?

04:12.753 --> 04:14.337
[footsteps departing]

04:17.216 --> 04:22.345
Just this once, make me happy
I gave birth to you, Maki.

04:23.471 --> 04:24.765
[metal clacks]

04:27.684 --> 04:28.852
[ripping]

04:38.653 --> 04:39.863
Father.

04:41.115 --> 04:42.365
[NAOYA]
You should've said something

04:42.407 --> 04:43.951
if you were
planning this from the get-go.

04:43.992 --> 04:46.494
[JINICHI]
You jumped the gun like always.

04:46.536 --> 04:49.998
Though I agree Megumi Fushiguro
would be better than you.

04:50.040 --> 04:51.332
[NAOYA] Excuse me?

04:51.374 --> 04:53.543
There's more than
a few voices pushing for him

04:53.585 --> 04:56.421
as a chance to repair
relations with the Gojo Clan.

04:56.463 --> 04:59.258
But you know there's no way
we could accept Fushiguro

04:59.298 --> 05:02.052
being entrusted with
all the money and cursed tools.

05:02.094 --> 05:03.887
[NAOYA] Then why
were you dilly-dallying?

05:03.929 --> 05:06.681
Because Fushiguro,
in addition to the Gojo Clan,

05:06.723 --> 05:08.307
has other alliances.

05:08.349 --> 05:11.770
He's friendly with Noritoshi,
the next head of the Kamo Clan.

05:11.812 --> 05:13.605
If we eliminate him
without cause,

05:13.647 --> 05:16.150
it would put the Zen'in Clan
in a worse spot.

05:16.191 --> 05:18.193
With Satoru Gojo sealed away,

05:18.235 --> 05:20.570
and the power balance between
clans shifting, we'll fall--

05:20.612 --> 05:23.282
I get all that, but what I don't
is why do it now?

05:23.322 --> 05:26.325
You haven't read the notices
from headquarters yet, have you?

05:26.660 --> 05:28.327
We can make use of that.

05:28.369 --> 05:31.414
Label them as traitors
plotting to release Satoru Gojo.

05:31.456 --> 05:34.626
And then Megumi,
Maki, and Mai can be killed.

05:34.668 --> 05:36.253
[laughs]

05:36.295 --> 05:37.545
That's an impressive plan.

05:37.587 --> 05:40.007
Killing his own daughters
adds believability.

05:40.048 --> 05:43.218
It will. Afterwards, the trust
that headquarters places in us

05:43.260 --> 05:45.262
- will grow firmer.
- [NAOYA] Hmm.

05:45.304 --> 05:47.889
And is old man Ogi
okay with all of this?

05:47.931 --> 05:49.891
[JINICHI]
Ogi came up with this plan.

05:49.933 --> 05:52.393
[OGI] There are no
cursed tools here, Maki.

05:52.435 --> 05:55.856
We emptied our vault in
anticipation of your intentions.

05:58.025 --> 06:01.695
[Mai grunting weakly]
Why did you come here?

06:01.736 --> 06:03.404
You idiot.

06:10.078 --> 06:14.291
JUZO KUMIYA'S MASTERPIECE,
THE CURSED TOOL "DRAGON BONE"

06:17.794 --> 06:20.588
SECRET ART:
FALLING BLOSSOM EMOTION

06:20.964 --> 06:23.925
[OGI] Do you know why they
named my older brother Naobito

06:23.967 --> 06:27.012
the previous head
of the clan, instead of me?

06:27.054 --> 06:28.763
[MAKI] I'm guessing
because you're an asshole

06:28.805 --> 06:30.557
who would murder
his own children.

06:33.601 --> 06:35.187
[swords swish, clang]

06:36.355 --> 06:37.564
[clangs]

06:45.488 --> 06:48.700
You never wondered why I was
passed over as head of the clan?

06:48.742 --> 06:49.951
[MAKI] How?

06:49.993 --> 06:52.162
[OGI] It was because
my two children...

06:52.204 --> 06:55.165
- [MAKI] I know I...
- ...were such hopeless failures!

06:55.207 --> 06:56.375
[MAKI]...broke his blade.

07:01.213 --> 07:03.840
- [footsteps]
- [dragging]

07:06.260 --> 07:07.928
[OGI] You broke my blade

07:07.969 --> 07:10.597
and judged that my reach
had been shortened,

07:10.638 --> 07:12.557
so you closed in on me.

07:12.599 --> 07:14.684
This is why you're hopeless.

07:15.185 --> 07:17.771
I'm not a swordsman,
I'm a sorcerer.

07:17.812 --> 07:20.357
Trying to gauge me by
the standards of such a failure

07:20.399 --> 07:22.067
is absolutely ridiculous.

07:22.109 --> 07:24.485
I'll say it
as many times as I must.

07:24.527 --> 07:27.488
I wasn't chosen to be
the previous head of the clan

07:27.530 --> 07:29.448
because of the two of you.

07:29.490 --> 07:32.451
My older brother's technique
was nothing to speak of.

07:32.493 --> 07:34.453
And his potential
to inherit the clan

07:34.495 --> 07:36.415
was never a point of contention.

07:36.455 --> 07:39.834
As a jujutsu sorcerer,
I never lagged behind my brother

07:39.876 --> 07:42.212
in any area except one.

07:42.254 --> 07:44.965
The quality of my two children.

07:46.216 --> 07:48.093
The one rule for children.

07:48.635 --> 07:50.845
Never drag down your parents.

07:51.346 --> 07:52.931
[MAI] Didn't you know?

07:52.973 --> 07:55.434
Dragging each other down
is considered a virtue

07:55.474 --> 07:56.684
in this country.

07:59.271 --> 08:00.981
[body rolling down]

08:03.482 --> 08:06.527
[OGI] This room is used
for training and punishment.

08:06.569 --> 08:08.196
We keep countless grade-two

08:08.238 --> 08:10.324
and lower cursed spirits
in here.

08:10.991 --> 08:13.327
They're hiding now
because they're afraid of me.

08:13.368 --> 08:14.828
But soon enough,
they'll crawl out

08:14.869 --> 08:16.495
and begin to devour you.

08:17.414 --> 08:20.875
A Heavenly Pact?
Enhanced physical prowess?

08:20.917 --> 08:22.127
What of it?

08:22.169 --> 08:24.296
We sorcerers train every day,

08:24.338 --> 08:26.173
and we further
strengthen our bodies

08:26.214 --> 08:29.134
with cursed energy and combat.

08:29.176 --> 08:32.304
Maki, your power's ordinary.

08:32.346 --> 08:35.390
What you possess, every
single one of us already has.

08:35.974 --> 08:39.311
Good riddance
to the sole stain on my life.

08:39.353 --> 08:41.104
[footsteps departing]

08:45.942 --> 08:47.361
[Mai grunts]

08:47.986 --> 08:51.448
[grunting]

09:16.014 --> 09:17.640
[MAI] Maki.

09:18.099 --> 09:19.642
You certainly are tough.

09:23.897 --> 09:25.440
I always figured

09:25.482 --> 09:28.151
it would come to this one day.

09:43.333 --> 09:44.834
This really sucks.

09:44.876 --> 09:46.503
[whooshing]

09:51.466 --> 09:52.591
[gasps]

09:53.510 --> 09:55.136
[ocean waves lapping]

10:11.361 --> 10:13.280
[MAI]
You basically know at this point

10:13.321 --> 10:15.031
what my technique can do, right?

10:15.656 --> 10:17.909
Although I still have trouble
creating anything

10:17.951 --> 10:19.869
too large or complicated.

10:23.164 --> 10:25.500
I'm wounded
from where he cut me, too.

10:25.542 --> 10:28.545
So after I create this,
I'll die.

10:28.587 --> 10:29.628
Later.

10:31.590 --> 10:33.300
Good luck on
your own after this.

10:33.341 --> 10:35.552
Hey. Mai, wait!

10:37.011 --> 10:40.515
What are you talking about?
Just come back here!

10:40.557 --> 10:42.225
[MAI] I've known
for a long time now

10:42.267 --> 10:45.437
why twins are considered to be
such an unfortunate accident

10:45.479 --> 10:47.188
by jujutsu sorcerers.

10:48.731 --> 10:51.818
You have to offer up something
in order to gain anything.

10:52.277 --> 10:54.154
This goes beyond just pacts.

10:54.195 --> 10:56.406
The fact that we go through
pain to grow stronger

10:56.448 --> 10:58.116
follows the same logic.

11:00.577 --> 11:03.455
But that balance
never functions properly

11:03.497 --> 11:05.624
in the case of twins like us.

11:07.000 --> 11:10.295
Because jujutsu
views identical twins

11:10.337 --> 11:12.005
as the same individual.

11:13.632 --> 11:15.091
Do you understand?

11:15.133 --> 11:17.844
You are me, and I am you.

11:18.553 --> 11:20.054
You can long to grow stronger

11:20.096 --> 11:22.516
and work so hard
you spit up blood.

11:23.057 --> 11:24.434
But it's all pointless.

11:24.976 --> 11:27.604
Because I don't want
to grow stronger at all.

11:29.230 --> 11:31.566
Even if you don't
have any techniques,

11:31.608 --> 11:33.568
it's pointless if I have one.

11:34.235 --> 11:38.323
So long as I exist, Maki,
you will always be incomplete.

11:38.365 --> 11:39.658
[MAKI] Okay, I get it!

11:40.534 --> 11:41.700
Just come back.

11:42.619 --> 11:44.703
[MAI] This is all
I'll leave you with.

11:44.745 --> 11:45.997
Cast off the rest.

11:46.039 --> 11:47.957
[♪ ethereal music playing]

11:50.418 --> 11:54.464
I'll take all the cursed energy
and everything else with me too.

11:55.798 --> 11:58.176
Just promise me one thing.

11:59.386 --> 12:02.805
Please... destroy everything.

12:05.600 --> 12:07.018
All of it, you hear?

12:09.270 --> 12:10.480
Big sister?

12:17.153 --> 12:18.238
[Maki distraughtly] Mai!

12:18.279 --> 12:19.531
Mai!

12:19.573 --> 12:20.657
Mai!

12:21.282 --> 12:23.868
Wake up! [sobs] Mai!

12:24.452 --> 12:27.205
Wake up! Mai!

12:28.039 --> 12:29.207
Wake up!

12:30.958 --> 12:32.460
[sobs] Mai?

12:33.670 --> 12:34.837
Mai.

12:35.255 --> 12:36.715
Wake up.

12:38.299 --> 12:39.384
Mai.

12:40.176 --> 12:42.721
Wake up, Mai.

12:46.891 --> 12:50.270
[Ogi gasps] The cursed spirits
were exorcised?

12:50.311 --> 12:51.812
What?

12:51.854 --> 12:53.356
My body remembers.

12:54.107 --> 12:57.860
I worked so hard
to forget that fear.

13:00.530 --> 13:03.450
Technique Release.
Blazing Courage!

13:03.491 --> 13:05.076
Very well then!

13:05.118 --> 13:06.869
This time, I'll burn you down,

13:06.911 --> 13:08.705
right to the marrow
of your bones

13:08.747 --> 13:10.039
with my own hands!

13:10.081 --> 13:11.458
[sword swishing]

13:12.459 --> 13:14.461
Come! You fail--

13:14.502 --> 13:16.630
[♪ calm ethereal music playing]

13:26.097 --> 13:27.265
Okay, Mai.

13:28.642 --> 13:29.892
Let's get started.

13:36.691 --> 13:39.944
EPISODE 51
PERFECT PREPARATION

13:40.445 --> 13:42.238
[metal clanging]

13:43.406 --> 13:44.865
JUJUTSU KAISEN

13:44.907 --> 13:47.327
[continues clanging]

13:48.411 --> 13:49.454
Ugh.

13:49.496 --> 13:51.205
Why is it so noisy?

13:51.748 --> 13:52.915
[yawns]

13:52.957 --> 13:55.502
[RANTA] Jinichi!
Maki has lost her mind!

13:55.543 --> 13:57.044
She murdered Ogi!

13:57.086 --> 13:59.838
The Kukuru Unit is on it now!

13:59.880 --> 14:02.133
I guess even Ogi
can be caught off-guard

14:02.175 --> 14:04.803
if he's attacked in his sleep
or sitting on the toilet.

14:05.136 --> 14:07.388
- Capture her before I get there.
- [KUKURU UNIT] Sir!

14:08.097 --> 14:10.891
If we dawdle too much,
Jinichi will become so smug,

14:10.933 --> 14:12.727
I'll never hear
the end of it from him.

14:13.060 --> 14:14.729
Oh, don't kill her yet.

14:14.771 --> 14:16.147
I'll finish her myself.

14:16.189 --> 14:17.231
[NARRATOR] The Kukuru Unit.

14:17.273 --> 14:18.983
The young men
of the Zen'in Clan

14:19.025 --> 14:21.820
who don't possess techniques
are obligated to join.

14:21.860 --> 14:24.823
And the martial arts are
drilled into them day and night

14:24.863 --> 14:26.783
so they can serve under the Hei.

14:26.825 --> 14:27.992
[NAOYA]
What are you going to do?

14:28.034 --> 14:29.703
[MAKI] I wonder
what I plan to do.

14:29.744 --> 14:32.580
[MAN 1] Visual confirmation of
two unidentified cursed tools!

14:32.622 --> 14:34.290
[NARRATOR]
Maki had also been a member

14:34.332 --> 14:36.626
until she joined Jujutsu High.

14:37.001 --> 14:41.047
[MAI] Why couldn't you just stay
at the bottom with me, Maki?

14:41.088 --> 14:43.383
- [MAKI] You were right.
- [MAN 2] Surround her!

14:43.424 --> 14:44.759
[MAKI] Staying at the bottom...

14:45.468 --> 14:48.054
I'm sure that would have
been the right choice for us.

14:49.263 --> 14:50.348
I'm sorry.

14:51.474 --> 14:53.184
- [MAKI] I'm sorry, Mai.
- [MAN 3] Get her!

14:53.226 --> 14:55.812
[MAI] Just promise me
one thing.

14:56.229 --> 14:58.565
Please destroy everything.

14:58.606 --> 15:00.650
[men grunting]

15:06.656 --> 15:08.324
[MAI] All of it, you hear?

15:09.576 --> 15:13.162
[men screaming]

15:13.204 --> 15:15.665
[men groaning]

15:18.292 --> 15:21.379
[grunting, groaning]

15:29.928 --> 15:31.556
[grunting]

15:33.182 --> 15:34.933
[groaning]

15:34.975 --> 15:38.855
[men groaning]

15:38.897 --> 15:41.107
[men groaning]

15:41.148 --> 15:42.525
[sword swishing]

15:42.567 --> 15:44.652
[groans]

15:44.694 --> 15:45.695
[grunts]

15:45.737 --> 15:49.574
[grunting, groaning]

15:54.621 --> 15:56.623
[grunting]

15:57.331 --> 15:59.250
[grunts, groans]

16:00.543 --> 16:02.044
[gasps, whimpers]

16:02.086 --> 16:06.006
[♪ upbeat rock music playing]

16:11.554 --> 16:16.225
[men groaning]

16:19.437 --> 16:23.149
[men gasping, groaning]

16:25.025 --> 16:26.653
[man groans]

16:29.906 --> 16:31.157
[sword slashing]

16:33.576 --> 16:34.993
[grunts]

16:37.246 --> 16:39.039
[grunts, groans]

16:42.209 --> 16:43.252
[gasps]

16:44.712 --> 16:45.964
[groans]

16:50.468 --> 16:53.554
[men whimpering]

16:56.891 --> 16:58.559
[grunts]

16:59.644 --> 17:01.019
[yells]

17:05.441 --> 17:08.820
[men groaning]

17:10.363 --> 17:12.949
[sword swishing]

17:22.834 --> 17:23.877
[sword clanks]

17:26.044 --> 17:28.422
[NOBUAKI] Hey,
how's it coming along?

17:29.298 --> 17:31.175
[gasps]

17:31.217 --> 17:33.511
She went for the jackpot.

17:37.473 --> 17:38.892
[loud crash]

17:43.103 --> 17:45.063
[♪ rock music playing]

18:00.788 --> 18:02.999
[NOBUAKI]
That's Chojuro's technique?

18:03.958 --> 18:05.418
The Hei are here.

18:05.459 --> 18:07.045
[NARRATOR] The Hei.

18:07.085 --> 18:09.047
They are composed of those
whose abilities are recognized

18:09.087 --> 18:12.633
as semi-grade one or higher
by Jujutsu High standards.

18:12.675 --> 18:16.345
The Zen'in Clan's strongest
collection of sorcerers.

18:20.058 --> 18:21.559
- [swords slash, clang]
- [grunts]

18:29.067 --> 18:30.317
[NOBUAKI]
How is she still moving

18:30.359 --> 18:31.945
after taking Chojuro's attack?

18:35.239 --> 18:36.323
[swords clanging]

18:36.699 --> 18:40.244
She's fast. Easily broke
through my guard! [groans]

18:41.913 --> 18:44.874
[CHOJURO] I don't believe it.
Is she really the same Maki?

18:44.916 --> 18:46.751
[groans]

19:00.932 --> 19:02.224
Jinichi!

19:02.725 --> 19:05.019
[JINICHI]
Keep holding her there, Ranta!

19:15.696 --> 19:17.031
[yells]

19:17.073 --> 19:18.992
I can't keep holding her!

19:19.700 --> 19:22.160
[Maki exhales]

19:22.202 --> 19:24.122
[RANTA]
Forget about me, Jinichi!

19:24.162 --> 19:26.206
The current
Zen'in Clan only exists

19:26.248 --> 19:27.792
thanks to the whim of Toji!

19:28.084 --> 19:30.003
You must have
realized it by now!

19:30.044 --> 19:32.672
Maki's become
the same as that man!

19:32.713 --> 19:35.091
Do it! Here and now!

19:35.133 --> 19:38.218
Kill her!

19:51.941 --> 19:54.192
[explosion]

20:06.330 --> 20:07.915
You did it, Jinichi.

20:08.374 --> 20:10.250
You were able to kill her.

20:17.091 --> 20:18.384
[blood splattering]

20:18.425 --> 20:20.136
[footsteps approaching]

20:26.184 --> 20:27.935
[NAOYA] How cruel of you.

20:27.977 --> 20:29.227
HEAD OF THE HEI, NAOYA ZEN'IN

20:29.269 --> 20:31.522
Have you no heart
left inside of you, Maki?

20:33.357 --> 20:34.483
I don't.

20:34.525 --> 20:36.736
She took
whatever heart I had with her.

20:37.570 --> 20:39.321
[NAOYA]
Everyone says I'm a genius.

20:39.363 --> 20:40.656
It's true, too!

20:40.990 --> 20:43.910
I'm going to be the head
of the clan after my father.

20:46.286 --> 20:48.748
I heard there's a loser
in the Zen'in Clan.

20:48.789 --> 20:50.833
They say the man ain't
got a bit of cursed energy

20:50.875 --> 20:52.501
in his whole body.

20:54.170 --> 20:56.130
He must be really depressed.

20:58.966 --> 21:01.552
I bet you that guy
looks pretty pathetic, too.

21:05.848 --> 21:08.017
[MAKI] Three, four,
five, nine, ten, eleven.

21:09.102 --> 21:10.436
[NAOYA] You...

21:14.148 --> 21:15.191
You...

21:19.361 --> 21:20.905
ain't no Toji!

21:22.615 --> 21:26.035
The sin of the insignificant
is the ignorance of strength.

21:26.452 --> 21:28.871
No one was able
to understand Toji.

21:30.873 --> 21:33.000
Except maybe Satoru Gojo.

21:33.500 --> 21:35.169
But you ain't the one!

21:35.211 --> 21:37.922
The one to stand
among them is me!

21:44.511 --> 21:46.013
[NARRATOR] Projection Sorcery

21:46.055 --> 21:47.681
can't be used
to create movements

21:47.723 --> 21:49.683
that ignore physics
and trajectories.

21:49.725 --> 21:52.352
There's a limit to how much
acceleration can be added

21:52.394 --> 21:54.272
to one's speed upon activation.

21:54.312 --> 21:56.857
The longer the technique
is continuously activated,

21:56.899 --> 21:59.068
the further one can
raise their speed.

21:59.359 --> 22:01.403
[NAOYA]
The one to stand among them

22:01.445 --> 22:02.655
is me!

22:11.538 --> 22:12.999
I won't stop now.

22:13.040 --> 22:15.501
I won't screw up
like I did back then!

22:15.835 --> 22:18.296
Force is weight times speed.

22:37.023 --> 22:39.192
She wants a head-on fight, huh?

22:39.692 --> 22:40.901
[MAKI] How about a hug?

22:40.943 --> 22:43.821
[NAOYA] I'll punch
through her at top speed!

22:47.700 --> 22:49.451
[NARRATOR] While
Projection Sorcery is active,

22:49.493 --> 22:51.245
anything the user touches
with their palm

22:51.287 --> 22:54.123
must create a movement
within 1/24th of a second.

22:54.165 --> 22:56.834
If they fail, they'll be
frozen for one second.

23:01.714 --> 23:03.799
[NAOYA] She was probably
planning to take my attack

23:03.841 --> 23:05.301
and stop my movement,

23:05.343 --> 23:07.636
even if it means
I break her ribs.

23:07.678 --> 23:10.264
Like I'd fall
for such obvious bait!

23:10.306 --> 23:12.099
You really are an imposter!

23:16.937 --> 23:18.564
24 times, right?

23:19.106 --> 23:21.525
You and old man Naobito
aren't just fast,

23:21.567 --> 23:23.736
there's something off
about your speed.

23:24.362 --> 23:27.240
You were creating
24 motions per second.

23:27.281 --> 23:29.867
I can finally see it
after obtaining this body.

23:30.868 --> 23:33.996
You imposter! [groans]

23:34.454 --> 23:35.622
[groans]

23:35.956 --> 23:36.999
[groans]

23:37.499 --> 23:38.542
[groans]

24:00.689 --> 24:01.941
Sorry.

24:02.691 --> 24:04.151
Can you repeat that?

24:05.361 --> 24:06.444
Mother?

24:11.075 --> 24:12.285
Mother?

24:21.001 --> 24:22.544
- Mother?
- [gasps]

24:22.586 --> 24:24.338
- Stay away!
- Mother.

24:24.380 --> 24:26.173
- Why must you?
- Please, listen to me.

24:26.215 --> 24:28.175
Why must you
always be like this?

24:28.217 --> 24:29.676
If that's the way you feel,

24:30.303 --> 24:31.595
why tell me to come back?

24:31.637 --> 24:33.889
Huh? W... What?

24:33.931 --> 24:35.473
What are you talking about?

24:37.268 --> 24:41.188
No. No, no, no! [whimpering]

24:41.230 --> 24:42.398
- [sword slashes]
- [groans]

24:42.440 --> 24:43.774
[thuds]

24:43.816 --> 24:46.902
[Naoya breathing raggedly]

24:46.944 --> 24:49.989
[gasping, laughing]

24:50.364 --> 24:52.699
Stupid bitch didn't end me.

24:53.117 --> 24:54.327
Pathetic.

24:54.368 --> 24:56.078
[breathing raggedly]

25:04.128 --> 25:07.465
[gasps] Are you shitting me?

25:07.505 --> 25:10.676
I can't focus my cursed energy!

25:10.717 --> 25:13.511
Damn gutter trash!

25:13.553 --> 25:14.596
[gasps]

25:16.182 --> 25:17.933
[exhales]

25:17.975 --> 25:19.435
[Mai and Maki giggling]

25:19.477 --> 25:22.520
[MAI AND MAKI'S MOTHER]
I'm glad I gave birth to you.

25:22.813 --> 25:25.523
[Momo running, panting]

25:27.193 --> 25:29.653
[MOMO] Mai! [sobbing]

25:35.242 --> 25:40.331
This is why
I told you not to go. [crying]

25:40.373 --> 25:42.708
[sobbing]

25:42.749 --> 25:45.752
[MAKI] Please,
take care of her.

25:45.794 --> 25:49.006
[MOMO] What are you
gonna do now, Maki?

25:51.884 --> 25:54.011
The six members of the Hei,
the nine members of the Akashi,

25:54.053 --> 25:55.553
and the 21 members
of the Kukuru Unit

25:55.595 --> 25:57.555
who were absent from
the Zen'in Clan's home that day

25:57.597 --> 25:58.807
all met untimely deaths.

25:58.849 --> 26:00.351
At present,
no residuals have been detected,

26:00.393 --> 26:02.144
and autopsies revealed
faint traces of cursed energy

26:02.186 --> 26:03.479
in the corpses' wounds
that are believed to come

26:03.521 --> 26:04.980
from the cursed tool
used as the murder weapon.

26:05.022 --> 26:06.648
Several days later, both
the Gojo Clan and Kamo Clan

26:06.690 --> 26:08.526
motioned for headquarters
to remove the Zen'in Clan

26:08.566 --> 26:09.651
from the big three families.

26:09.693 --> 26:10.861
Headquarters has tabled
this motion.

26:20.204 --> 26:22.373
[♪ closing theme song playing]

27:50.419 --> 27:51.962
[MEGUMI]
Hakari was expelled for clashing

27:52.004 --> 27:53.755
- with the Upper Brass.
- [YUJI] A fight club?

27:53.797 --> 27:55.424
[MACHO] You don't
talk about the fight club.

27:55.466 --> 27:56.967
[PANDA] I can't get close.

27:57.009 --> 27:58.844
[MEGUMI] Itadori, you
snoop around from the inside.

27:58.885 --> 28:00.471
[KIRARA] I love it
when you're hot, Kin.

28:00.513 --> 28:03.223
[KINJI] Are you saying you
wanna get high on my passion?

28:03.265 --> 28:04.975
NEXT EPISODE
PASSION
